The paper deals with communication over a noisy channel with feedback, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). The use of linear quadratic Gaussian optimal control theory suggests that the paper may also fall under the sub-category of systems and control (cs.SY). The paper involves the use of mathematical tools and algorithms, which could place it under the sub-categories of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) or multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper may also fall under the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) due to the use of optimization techniques.
